			<div class="corrections ">
					</div>
			<h1 property="dc.title">Apple expected to delve into textbooks</h1>
			<div class="relative primary-slot padding-top img-border gallery-container photo-wrapper">
					<a href="/business/economy/tablet-wars-intensify/2011/05/02/AFPKCmzF_gallery.html"><img class="gallery-pic" src="/rf/image_606w/2010-2019/WashingtonPost/2012/01/18/National-Economy/Images/ipad.JPG" /></a>
					<a href="/business/economy/tablet-wars-intensify/2011/05/02/AFPKCmzF_gallery.html"><span class="tool Gallery-play hide"></span></a>
				</div>
				<div class="gallery-caption border-bottom relative">
					<span class="gallery-credit"></span>
					<p class="caption padding-left border-left"><a class="gallery-link" href="/business/economy/tablet-wars-intensify/2011/05/02/AFPKCmzF_gallery.html"><strong>View Photo Gallery &mdash;</strong> &thinsp;It seems like a new tablet hits the market every day. Here&rsquo;s a look at a few that are vying for people&rsquo;s attention.</a></p>
				</div>
			<div class="module article-toolbar relative border-bottom padding-top-8 padding-bottom-8  margin-bottom-20 ">
	<ul class="inline-list">
		<li class="text-size">
			<a href="#" class="text-size-control"><img class="text-size-control-smaller" src="/rw/sites/twpweb/img/icons/icon-minus.png" alt="Smaller Text" /></a>
